Over 64, 40-foot containers will be housed at the Park expected to attract very important personalities from car manufacturers, diplomats to business magnates.A special mixed zone for mandatory media interviews has been created while the WRC Safari team has identified the KWS land opposite the institute, as the parking area for the fans. The World Rally Championship Safari Rally route will be certified by the International Automobile federation (FIA) in the coming weeks.
As I indicated in this column last week, the rally has a mixture of “bad” and “good” roads. 
Diversions have been created in straight stretches at the Soysambu Conservancy to reduce speeds that are likely to hit over 200 kilometres per hour.



